reviews.review_text:
Best Aud of the3 Less tinny, but the Crap Centre was not the best sounding venue. They use to put relay speakers out in the hallway and I use to have a copy of one recorded from those.  Real clean, and plenty of room to dance. Charlie Miller, do you have a SB you can DL for us???

show and recording about a 3.75. Only reason I want it cause I was there.
